      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THAI TIGER (8) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from five starts. Below best last time at Shepparton (22.74) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4 length fifth. Rates a leading player. JED'S MEMORY (7) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 24.37 beating Paw Enna. Sure to be thereabouts. JACKY SON (1) failed to feature last start at this track, but prior to that won by 1.2 lengths at Healesville (19.63) beating Snapper Head in a T3 RSTW on February 6. Expected to feature in the finish. SHREK'S BROTHER (2) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
